description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Parvati purrs with a rating of 74, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 592, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Leverage for East, 3 for South, and Stringalong for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40748-46372-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [592 Votes, Hall of Fame]
